## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="538f6-102">可以为任何已安装的语音识别器创建此类的实例。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="538f6-102">You can create an instance of this class for any of the installed speech recognizers.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="538f6-103">若要获取有关已安装的识别器的信息，请使用 static <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.InstalledRecognizers%2A> 方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="538f6-103">To get information about which recognizers are installed, use the static <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.InstalledRecognizers%2A> method.</span></span>  
  
