 <span data-ttu-id="538f6-115"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine> 对象用于唯一使用实例化对象的进程。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="538f6-115">The <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine> object is for the sole use of the process that instantiated the object.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="538f6-116">与此相反，<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer> 与想要使用它的任何应用程序共享单个识别器。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="538f6-116">By contrast, the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer> shares a single recognizer with any application that wants to use it.</span></span>  
  
