## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="538f6-638">下面的示例获取当前进程内语音识别引擎的部分数据列表。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="538f6-638">The following example gets a partial list of data for the current in-process speech recognition engine.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="538f6-639">有关详细信息，请参阅 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizerInfo>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="538f6-639">For more information, see <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizerInfo>.</span></span>  
  
